SEC. 1935. CONIo'Iml':NCE PARTICIPANTS.
In order to carry out the purposes and responsibilities specified in sections 1933 and 1934, the Conference shall bring together individuals concerned with issues relating to drug abuse education, prevention, and treatment, and the production, trafficking, and distribution ofillicit drugs. The President shall-
